config.script:
# Sets the selected custom property, which determines whether the
	# unit controls or system controls are displayed.
	
	self.parent.parent.parent.getChild("Header").custom.selected = 0

# Sets the selected custom property, which determines whether the
	# unit controls or system controls are displayed.
	
	self.parent.parent.parent.getChild("Header").custom.selected = 1

# Open the mobile side menu.
	
	system.perspective.openDock('sideMenu')

# Display dock that displays the roof.
		
	system.perspective.openDock('roofDisplay',params={})
